{
  "slug": "superpowers",
  "name": "Superpowers",
  "type": "plugin",
  "description": "Core skills library for Claude Code: TDD, debugging, collaboration patterns, and proven techniques",
  "longDescription": "Skills library by Jesse Vincent with **14 skills**, **1 agent**, **3 commands**, and a session-start hook.\n\n- **Skills**: TDD (with anti-patterns doc), systematic debugging (root cause tracing, defense in depth), subagent-driven development, code review (requesting and receiving), git worktrees, plan writing, brainstorming, parallel agent dispatch, verification before completion\n- **Commands**: `/brainstorm`, `/write-plan`, `/execute-plan`\n- **Agent**: code-reviewer",
  "compatibility": [
    "claude"
  ],
  "pluginType": "package",
